defOutLefNDR(25.10)                                        defOutLefNDR(25.10)

Name
       defOutLefNDR

Syntax
        defOutLefNDR{0 | 1}

       Type: Integer

       Default: 0

       Controls  whether defOut writes out LEF non-default rule information in
       DEF. By default, defOut does not write out non-default rules defined in
       LEF.

Related Information
              * defOut

              * defOutBySection

